---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Investment & Acquisition Partners — Trion Holdings" description="Explore Trion Holdings' network of investment and acquisition partners—industry leaders supporting scalable growth across hospitality, consumer brands, tech, and real estate.">
  <main>

    <!-- Top Banner -->
    <section class="relative flex min-h-[50vh] md:min-h-[70vh] w-full items-center justify-center bg-cover bg-top" style="background-image: url('/ttp-register-banner.jpg');">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-[#1A1919]/80 via-[#1A1919]/65 to-[#1A1919]"></div>
      <div class="relative z-10 max-w-3xl px-4 mb-20 mt-52 text-center text-white">
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold sm:text-5xl md:text-6xl">Investment &amp; Acquisition Partners</h1>
        <p class="mt-4 text-lg sm:text-xl">We've built strong relationships with industry leaders across multiple sectors to provide comprehensive support for our portfolio companies.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Section Separator -->
    <div>
      <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 1440 193"><path fill="#e3ba63" d="m0 74.286 987.143 46.19L980 169.048 0 186.667z"/><path fill="#1a1919" d="M0 0h1440v64.286l-221.43 128.571L0 76.191z"/></svg>
    </div>

    <!-- Intro two-column -->
    <section class="bg-white px-4 py-16 md:py-28 color-copy">
      <div class="max-width mx-auto flex flex-row flex-wrap md:flex-nowrap gap-12 items-center justify-between">
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
          <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-4">Building Value Through Partnership</h2>
          <div class="w-20 h-1 bg-[#E3BA63] mb-6"></div>
          <p class="leading-6 mb-4">At Trion Holdings, partnerships are at the heart of what we do. Over the past 45+ years, we've built strong relationships with entrepreneurs, operators, and industry leaders across a wide range of sectors. Our goal is simple: to bring expertise and a powerful network together so businesses can scale smarter, grow faster, and unlock their full potential.</p>
          <p class="leading-6 mb-4">Our portfolio reflects our diverse approach—ranging from hospitality concepts and consumer brands to tech startups and real estate. In real estate, we remain deeply rooted in New York and Connecticut, investing in everything from large multifamily and mixed-use properties to unique individual homes and property management companies.</p>
          <p class="leading-6">We take pride in working with people who share our vision for growth, creativity, and value creation. Whether it's helping a restaurant expand, supporting an emerging brand, or repositioning a property, our partnerships are built to last and designed for impact.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
          <img src="/trion-management-building.webp" alt="Trion partners collaborating" class="w-full h-auto object-cover" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="800" height="533" />
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>


    <section class="px-4">
        <div class="max-width mx-auto flex flex-row flex-wrap md:flex-nowrap gap-12 items-center justify-between">
            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
                <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl md:text-5xl mb-4">Our Partners</h2>
                <p>We collaborate with a diverse group of partners who bring specialized expertise and resources to the table. From marketing and branding agencies to technology providers and logistics experts, our partners help us address challenges and seize opportunities more effectively.</p>
            </div>


            <div class="w-full md:w-1/2">
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 content-center gap-y-6  items-center">
                    <img src="/trion-real-estate-management-logo.webp" alt="Trion Real Estate Management logo" class="max-w-[62px] mx-auto" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="266" height="384" />                    
                    <img src="/thetacoproject-logo.webp" alt="The Taco Project logo" class="max-w-[71px] mx-auto col-span-1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="71" height="70" />
                    <img src="/airbnb-logo.webp" alt="Airbnb logo" class="max-w-[162px] mx-auto" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="128" height="43" />
                    <img src="/april-marin-logo.webp" alt="April Marin logo" class="max-w-[146px] mx-auto col-span-1" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="146" height="51" />
                    <img src="/gipper-logo.webp" alt="Gipper logo" class="max-w-[149px] mx-auto" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="149" height="40" />
                    <img src="/credready-logo.webp" alt="CredReady logo" class="max-w-[145px] mx-auto" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="145" height="45" />
                    <img src="/milio-realty-corp.webp" alt="Milio Realty Corp logo" class="max-w-[160px] mx-auto" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="422" height="72" />
                    <img src="/silversands-logo.svg" alt="Silver Sands logo" class="max-w-[145px] mx-auto" loading="lazy" decoding="async" width="145" height="24" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

    </section>

  </main>
</Base>